<!--/noindex-->
<p class="legend ShowFluff">Fromout of blacknessthey come, emerging from the depths of the realms’seas upon a surging tide of magic. Thesemerciless raidersdo not seek merely to slaughteror enslave, however, for they are the Idoneth Deepkin – they havecome to take their victims’ verysouls.</p>
This page contains all of the rules you need to field your Idoneth Deepkin miniatures on the battlefields of the Mortal Realms, from a host of exciting allegiance abilities to a range of warscrolls and warscroll battalions. The rules are split into the following sections.<ul></ul>
<div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;"><div class="BreakInsideAvoid Corner3" style="padding:0px;max-width:988px;"><table class="frameDark collapse" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" ><tbody><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_1.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_2.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_3.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_8.png" style="width:20px"></td><td bgcolor="#1d190d" style="color:#fefefe"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif; font-size:1em"><div class="contents_header">Contents</div><div class="NavColumns3"><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin#Books" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>ooks</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin#Designers-Commentary" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">D</b>esigners’ Commentary</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin#Battletome:-Idoneth-Deepkin" style="color:#fefefe">Battletome: Idoneth Deepkin</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Allies" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>llies</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Battle-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">B</b>attle Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Forgotten-Nightmares" style="color:#fefefe">Forgotten Nightmares</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Tides-of-Death" style="color:#fefefe">Tides of Death</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Command-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">C</b>ommand Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Artefacts-of-Power" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">A</b>rtefacts of Power</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Akhelian-Artefacts" style="color:#fefefe">Akhelian Artefacts</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Idoneth-Artefacts" style="color:#fefefe">Idoneth Artefacts</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Isharann-Artefacts" style="color:#fefefe">Isharann Artefacts</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Arcane-Artefacts" style="color:#fefefe">Arcane Artefacts</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Spell-Lores" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">S</b>pell Lores</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Lore-of-the-Deeps" style="color:#fefefe">Lore of the Deeps</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#The-Ethersea" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">T</b>he Ethersea</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Isharann-Rituals" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">I</b>sharann Rituals</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Ritual-of-Erosion" style="color:#fefefe">Ritual of Erosion</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Ritual-of-Rousing" style="color:#fefefe">Ritual of Rousing</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Ritual-of-the-Tempest" style="color:#fefefe">Ritual of the Tempest</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Mount-Traits" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">M</b>ount Traits</a><img class="tooltip logo2" title="Expansion. Broken Realms: Morathi (2th edition, version 1.0)" src="/aos/img/expansions/BR_logo2.png"></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Deepmare-Mount-Traits" style="color:#fefefe">Deepmare Mount Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Leviadon-Mount-Traits" style="color:#fefefe">Leviadon Mount Traits</a></div><div class="mw1 i10"><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#The-Enclaves" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">T</b>he Enclaves</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Ionrach" style="color:#fefefe">Ionrach</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</