/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Path-to-Glory" style="color:#fefefe"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>ath to Glory</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Idoneth-Deepkin-Warband-Tables" style="color:#fefefe">Idoneth Deepkin Warband Tables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/idoneth-deepkin/#Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Champion Rewards Table</a></div></div></span></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_4.png" style="width:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_7.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_6.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_5.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
